    "text": "```python\nAnalysis.AbaqusStep.StaticStep(strName=\"\", strDescription=\"\", iAutomatic=0, iMaxInc=0, dInitSize=0.0, dMinSize=0.0, dMaxSize=0.0, iMethod=0, iMatrixStorage=0, iSolutionTech=0, iAllowIter=0, dAdjustFactor=0.0, iMaxContactIteration=0, iType=0, dDampingFactor=0.0, iUseAdaptive=0, dMaxRationOfEnergyStrain=0.0, iNlGeom=0, dTimePeriod=0.0, iIncludeHeatEffect=0, iConvertDiscontinuityIteration=0, iRamp=0, iExtrapolateMethod=0, iAcceptByMaxIteration=0, iObtainLongTermSolution=0, iPertubation=0, iFullPlasticRegion=0, strlFullPlasticRegion=[], listOutput=[], crEdit=None)\n```\n\n## Description\n\nCreate Abaqus step for General Static analysis.\n\n## Inputs\n\n### `strName`\n\n- A _String_ specifying the Static step name.\n- The default value is \"\".\n\n### `strDescription`\n\n- A _String_ specifying the Static step description.\n- The default value is \"\".\n\n### `iAutomatic`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the increment method.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iMaxInc`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the maximum number of increments.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `dInitSize`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the initial increment size.\n- The default value is 0.0.\n\n### `dMinSize`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the minimum increment size.\n- The default value is 0.0.\n\n### `dMaxSize`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the maximum increment size.\n- The default value is 0.0.\n\n### `iMethod`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the equation solver method.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iMatrixStorage`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the equation solver matrix storage setting.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iSolutionTech`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the solution technique.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iAllowIter`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the number of iterations allowed before the kernel matrix is reformed.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `dAdjustFactor`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the adjustment factor for the number of solutions in each iteration.\n- The default value is 0.0.\n\n### `iMaxContactIteration`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the maximum number of contact iterations.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iType`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the automatic static stabilization.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `dDampingFactor`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the damping factor for automatic static stabilization.\n- The default value is 0.0.\n\n### `iUseAdaptive`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying whether or not to use adaptive stabilization.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `dMaxRationOfEnergyStrain`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the maximum ratio of stabilization to strain energy.\n- The default value is 0.0.\n\n### `iNlGeom`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying whether or not to consider geometric nonlinear (large deformation) analysis.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `dTimePeriod`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the analysis time.\n- The default value is 0.0.\n\n### `iIncludeHeatEffect`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying whether or not to consider adiabatic heating effects.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iConvertDiscontinuityIteration`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the conversion of severe discontinuity iterations.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iRamp`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the number of linear change over step.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iExtrapolateMethod`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the extrapolate previous state at start of each increment.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iAcceptByMaxIteration`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying whether or not to accept the solution after reaching maximum number of iterations.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iObtainLongTermSolution`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying whether or not to obtain long-term solution.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iPertubation`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying whether or not to apply perturbation.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iFullPlasticRegion`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying whether or not to check the full plastic region.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `strlFullPlasticRegion`\n\n- A _List of String_ specifying the full plastic region table list.\n- The default value is [].\n\n### `listOutput`\n\n- An _[ABAQUS_OUTPUT_REQUEST](./../../data-type/psj-command/parameter-types/ABAQUS_OUTPUT_REQUEST)_ list specifying the list of Abaqus output request.\n- The default value is _[ABAQUS_OUTPUT_REQUEST](./../../data-type/psj-command/parameter-types/ABAQUS_OUTPUT_REQUEST)_.\n\n### `crEdit`\n\n- A _Cursor_ specifying an existing Abaqus step.\n  - If this parameter is used, the specified step will be modified.\n  - If it is left _None_, a new step will be created.\n- The default value is _None_.\n\n## Return Code\n\nA _Cursor_ specifying the created/modified Abaqus Static step.\n\n## Sample Code\n\n```psj {43-58}\nimport os\n# Prepare a model\nGeometry.Part.Cube(ilAxialNodes=[3, 3, 3],\n                   iPartColor=7463537)\nMeshing.SolidMeshing(crlParts=[Part(1)],\n                     dGradingFactor=1.05,\n                     iSpeedVsQual=1,\n                     iRegion=1,\n                     bSafeMode=False,\n                     iParallel=16,\n                     bInternalMeshOnly=False,\n                     iPartColor=65280)\nBoundaryConditions.Pressure.General(strName=\"Pressure_1\",\n                                    dPressure=100000000.0,\n                                    crlTargets=[Face(26)])\nBoundaryConditions.FixedConstraint(strName=\"Constraint_1\",\n                                   crlTargets=[Face(25)])\nProperties.Material.Add(\n  strMaterialName=\"Copper_Alloy\",\n  dictMaterialProperty={\n    'Density': {'density': {'DENSITY': [8300.0]}},\n    'Elastic': {\n      'elastic': {\n        'YOUNGS_MODULUS': [110000000000.0],\n        'POISSONS_RATIO': [0.34]}},\n    'Expansion': {'expansion': {'ALPHA': [1.8e-05]}},\n    'Conductivity': {'conductivity': {'CONDUCTIVITY': [385.0]}},\n    'SpecificHeat': {'specificHeat': {'SPECIFIC_HEAT': [419.0]}}},\n  iMaterialID=1,\n  iMaterialColor=7901428)\nProperties.Solid(crlTargets=[Part(1)],\n                 strName=\"SolidProperty_1\",\n                 iPropertyColor=16131973,\n                 crMaterial=Material(1),\n                 iCordM=-2,\n                 dDynaRemeshVal1=DFLT_DBL,\n                 dDynaRemeshVal2=DFLT_DBL,\n                 dDispHG=DFLT_DBL,\n                 iFLG=-1)\nJPT.ViewFitToModel()\n\n# Prepare General Static Step\nAnalysis.AbaqusStep.StaticStep(strName=\"Step1\",\n                               iAutomatic=1,\n                               iMaxInc=100,\n                               dInitSize=1.0,\n                               dMinSize=1e-05,\n                               dMaxSize=1.0,\n                               iAllowIter=8,\n                               dAdjustFactor=1.0,\n                               iMaxContactIteration=30,\n                               dDampingFactor=0.0002,\n                               iUseAdaptive=1,\n                               dMaxRationOfEnergyStrain=0.05,\n                               dTimePeriod=1.0,\n                               iRamp=1,\n                               iExtrapolateMethod=1,\n                               strlFullPlasticRegion=[\"\"])\nAnalysis.ModifyLbcToStep(\n  listAbaqusLbcStepInfo=[\n    ABAQUS_LBC_STEP_INFO(crStep=AbaqStepsStructStatic(1),\n                         crLbc=LbcConstraint(1),\n                         iCurflag=2),\n    ABAQUS_LBC_STEP_INFO(crStep=AbaqStepsStructStatic(1),\n                         crLbc=LbcGPressure(1),\n                         iCurflag=3,\n                         iPreflag=2)])\n\n# Create an Abaqus job\nAnalysis.Abaqus(strName=\"Job_1\",\n                abaqusAnalysis=JOB_ABAQUS_DATA(\n                  iUnit=1,\n                  crDummyMat=Material(1),\n                  bWriteHistoryInSeparateFile=True),\n                crlStepSequence=[AbaqStepsStructStatic(1)])\n\n# Export an Abaqus file\ntemp_path = JPT.GetAppPathInfo(JPT.PathType.TEMP_PATH)\nAnalysis.ExportAbaqus(crAbaJob=AbaqusJob(1),\n                      strInpPath=os.path.join(temp_path,\n                                              \"Job_1.inp\"))\n```"
