    "text": "```python\nAnalysis.ACTRAN.ExportBdf(strPath=\"\")\n```\n\n## Description\n\n## Inputs\n\n### `strPath`\n\n- A _String_ specifying the destination path file to export.\n- The default value is \"\".\n\n## Return Code\n\nA String of 1 if success, or 0 if fail.\n\n## Sample Code\n\n```psj\nAnalysis.ACTRAN.ExportBdf(strPath=\"Job1.bdf\")\n```"
