    "text": "```python\nManual2D.MergeElement.TwoQuadsToQuad(crlElems)\n```\n\n## Description\n\nMerge two Quad elements into one Quad element.\n\n## Inputs\n\n### `crlElems`\n\n- A _List of Cursor_ specifying the element will be merged.\n- This is a required input.\n\n## Return Code\n\nA String of 1 if success, or 0 if fail.\n\n## Sample Code\n\n```psj {11}\nGeometry.Part.Cube(iPartColor=13259210)\nMeshing.GridMesh(\n    listGridMesh=[\n        GRID_MESH(crlFace=[Face(26)], crlCorner=[Node(6, 7, 8, 5)], \n        ilMeshCount=[9, 9], \n        iShape=4, \n        iElemtype=4, \n        bLocalSetting=True)], \n    bProjectToCad=True, \n    strGroupName=\"GridMeshFace\")\nMeshCleanup.Manual2D.MergeElement.TwoQuadsToQuad(crlElems=[Elem(1113, 1122)])\n```"
