    "text": "```python\nMeshCleanup.Manual2D.DeleteElement(crlElems, bKeepShareElem=False)\n```\n\n## Description\n\nDelete Tri/Quad Element.\n\n## Inputs\n\n### `crlElems`\n\n- A _List of Cursor_ specifying the element to be deleted.\n- This is a required input.\n\n### `bKeepShareElem`\n\n- A _Boolean_ specifying whether to keep shared element.\n- The default value is False.\n\n## Return Code\n\nA String of 1 if success, or 0 if fail.\n\n## Sample Code\n\n```psj {2}\nGeometry.Part.Cube(iPartColor=6409934)\nMeshCleanup.Manual2D.DeleteElement(crlElems=[Elem(1058, 1055)])\n```"
