    "text": "```python\nMeshEdit.MoveNode.AlongEdge(crlNodes=[], bMoveX=False, bMoveY=False, bMoveZ=False, dPosX=0.0, dPosY=0.0, dPosZ=0.0, iMoveType=0)\n```\n\n## Description\n\nMove nodes to a specified coordinate position along an edge.\n\n## Inputs\n\n### `crlNodes`\n\n- A _List of Cursor_ specifying the target nodes to move.\n- The default value is [].\n\n### `bMoveX`\n\n- A _Boolean_ specifying whether to move along the X axis.\n- The default value is False.\n\n### `bMoveY`\n\n- A _Boolean_ specifying whether to move along the Y axis.\n- The default value is False.\n\n### `bMoveZ`\n\n- A _Boolean_ specifying whether to move along the Z axis.\n- The default value is False.\n\n### `dPosX`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the target X coordinate.\n- The default value is 0.0.\n\n### `dPosY`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the target Y coordinate.\n- The default value is 0.0.\n\n### `dPosZ`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the target Z coordinate.\n- The default value is 0.0.\n\n### `iMoveType`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the movement type.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n## Return Code\n\nReturns a string \"1\" if successful, or \"0\" if failed.\n\n## Sample Code\n\n```psj\nGeometry.Part.Cube(ilAxialNodes=[6, 6, 6], iPartColor=15658599)\nJPT.Exec('ViewShowMesh(1)')\nJPT.ViewFitToModel()\n\nMeshEdit.MoveNode.AlongEdge(crlNodes=[Node(41,42,43,44)], bMoveX=True, dPosX=0.005)\n```"
