    "text": "```python\nACModeling.Cut(crlParts)\n```\n\n## Description\n\nCut for ACModeling\n\n## Inputs\n\n### `crlParts`\n\n- A _List of Cursor_ specifying the part.\n- This is a required input.\n\n## Return Code\n\nA String of 1 if success, or 0 if fail.\n\n## Sample Code\n\n```psj\nACModeling.Cut(crlParts)\n```"
