  "Analysis.LSDYNAJob": {
    "prefix": "LSDYNAJob",
    "signature": "Analysis.LSDYNAJob(crEdit=None)",
    "params": [
      "crEdit=None"
    ],
    "text": "```python\nAnalysis.LSDYNAJob(crEdit=None)\n```\n\n## Description\n\nCreate LS-Dyna Analysis Job.\n\n## Inputs\n\n### `crEdit`\n\n- A _Cursor_ specifying the existing analysis job to modify instead of creating a new one.\n- The default value is None.\n\n### `iTypeAnalysis`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the type of analysis.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iTypeSolver`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the type of solver.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `jobSetting`\n\n- A _[JOB_SETTING](./../../data-type/psj-command/parameter-types/JOB_SETTING)_ specifying the job settings including job name, description, termination condition and time step control.\n- The default value is _JOB_SETTING()_.\n\n### `outputSetting`\n\n- An _[OUTPUT_SETTING](./../../data-type/psj-command/parameter-types/OUTPUT_SETTING)_ specifying the output settings including file output frequency and various output options.\n- The default value is _OUTPUT_SETTING()_.\n\n### `relaxation`\n\n- A _[RELAXATION](./../../data-type/psj-command/parameter-types/RELAXATION)_ specifying the relaxation settings.\n- The default value is _RELAXATION()_.\n\n### `viscosity`\n\n- A _[VISCOSITY](./../../data-type/psj-command/parameter-types/VISCOSITY)_ specifying the viscosity settings including quadratic and linear artificial viscosity coefficients and hourglass type.\n- The default value is _VISCOSITY()_.\n\n### `loadCase`\n\n- A _[LOAD_CASE](./../../data-type/psj-command/parameter-types/LOAD_CASE)_ specifying the load case settings.\n- The default value is _LOAD_CASE()_.\n\n### `control`\n\n- A _[CONTROL](./../../data-type/psj-command/parameter-types/CONTROL)_ specifying the control settings including contact parameters.\n- The default value is _CONTROL()_.\n\n### `solid`\n\n- A _[SOLID](./../../data-type/psj-command/parameter-types/SOLID)_ specifying the solid element control settings.\n- The default value is _SOLID()_.\n\n### `output`\n\n- An _[OUTPUT](./../../data-type/psj-command/parameter-types/OUTPUT)_ specifying the output control settings.\n- The default value is _OUTPUT()_.\n\n### `mpp`\n\n- An _[MPP](./../../data-type/psj-command/parameter-types/MPP)_ specifying the MPP (Massively Parallel Processing) decomposition settings.\n- The default value is _MPP()_.\n\n## Return Code\n\nA _Boolean_ specifying the status of the job creation:\n\n- _True_: The LS-Dyna analysis job has been created successfully.\n- _False_: The LS-Dyna analysis job cannot be created.\n\n## Sample Code\n\n```psj{42-53}\nimport os\n\n# Create a model\nGeometry.Part.Cube(ilAxialNodes=[3, 3, 3], iPartColor=7463537)\nMeshing.SolidMeshing(crlParts=[Part(1)],\n                     dGradingFactor=1.05,\n                     iSpeedVsQual=1,\n                     iRegion=1,\n                     bSafeMode=False,\n                     iParallel=16,\n                     bInternalMeshOnly=False,\n                     iPartColor=65280)\nBoundaryConditions.Pressure.General(strName=\"Pressure_1\",\n                                    dPressure=100000000.0,\n                                    crlTargets=[Face(26)])\nBoundaryConditions.FixedConstraint(strName=\"Constraint_1\",\n                                   crlTargets=[Face(25)])\nProperties.Material.Add(\n    strMaterialName=\"Copper_Alloy\",\n    dictMaterialProperty={\n        'Density': {'density': {'DENSITY': [8300.0]}},\n        'Elastic': {'elastic': {'YOUNGS_MODULUS': [110000000000.0],\n                                'POISSONS_RATIO': [0.34]}},\n        'Expansion': {'expansion': {'ALPHA': [1.8e-05]}},\n        'Conductivity': {'conductivity': {'CONDUCTIVITY': [385.0]}},\n        'SpecificHeat': {'specificHeat': {'SPECIFIC_HEAT': [419.0]}}\n    },\n    iMaterialID=1,\n    iMaterialColor=7901428)\nProperties.Solid(crlTargets=[Part(1)],\n                 strName=\"SolidProperty_1\",\n                 iPropertyColor=16131973,\n                 crMaterial=Material(1),\n                 iCordM=-2,\n                 dDynaRemeshVal1=DFLT_DBL,\n                 dDynaRemeshVal2=DFLT_DBL,\n                 dDispHG=DFLT_DBL,\n                 iFLG=-1)\nJPT.ViewFitToModel()\n\n# Export as a LS-Dyna(.k) file\nAnalysis.LSDYNAJob(\n    iTypeAnalysis=1,\n    iTypeSolver=3,\n    jobSetting=JOB_SETTING(\n        strJobName=\"Job_1\",\n        termination=TERMINATION(),\n        timeStepControl=TIME_STEP_CONTROL()\n    ),\n    outputSetting=OUTPUT_SETTING(),\n    loadCase=LOAD_CASE(),\n    control=CONTROL()\n)\ntemp_folder = JPT.GetAppPathInfo(JPT.PathType.TEMP_PATH)\nAnalysis.ExportLsdyna(\n    strPath=os.path.join(temp_folder, \"Job_1.k\"),\n    crJob=LSDynaJob(1))\n```"
  },
