  "MeshEdit.Face": {
    "prefix": "Face",
    "signature": "MeshEdit.Face(crlFaces, crlFaceFixed, iOffsetType=0, crCoord=None, dlOffset=[1.0, 0.0, 0.0], dOffset=0, iDistType=0, dDistStrong=10, dDistWeak=20, iNodeIdPick=-1, dlPickForMacro=[])",
    "params": [
      "crlFaces",
      "crlFaceFixed",
      "iOffsetType=0",
      "crCoord=None",
      "dlOffset=[1.0, 0.0, 0.0]",
      "dOffset=0",
      "iDistType=0",
      "dDistStrong=10",
      "dDistWeak=20",
      "iNodeIdPick=-1",
      "dlPickForMacro=[]"
    ],
    "text": "```python\nMeshEdit.Face(crlFaces, crlFaceFixed, iOffsetType=0, crCoord=None, dlOffset=[1.0, 0.0, 0.0], dOffset=0, iDistType=0, dDistStrong=10, dDistWeak=20, iNodeIdPick=-1, dlPickForMacro=[])\n```\n\n## Description\n\nExecute morphing deformation by specifying faces to move.\n\n## Inputs\n\n### `crlFaces`\n\n- A _List of Cursor_ specifying the faces to move.\n- This is a required input.\n\n### `crlFaceFixed`\n\n- A _List of Cursor_ specifying the fixed faces.\n- This is a required input.\n\n### `iOffsetType`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the offset type.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `crCoord`\n\n- A _Cursor_ specifying the local coordinate system.\n- The default value is None.\n\n### `dlOffset`\n\n- A _List of Double_ specifying the offset direction vector.\n- The default value is [1.0, 0.0, 0.0].\n\n### `dOffset`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the offset amount.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `iDistType`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the influence distance type.\n- The default value is 0.\n\n### `dDistStrong`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the strong influence distance.\n- The default value is 10.\n\n### `dDistWeak`\n\n- A _Double_ specifying the weak influence distance.\n- The default value is 20.\n\n### `iNodeIdPick`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the node ID for GUI pick.\n- The default value is -1.\n\n### `dlPickForMacro`\n\n- A _List of Double_ specifying the GUI pick position for macro recording.\n- The default value is [].\n\n## Return Code\n\nReturns a string \"1\" if successful, or \"0\" if failed.\n\n## Sample Code\n\n```psj\nGeometry.Part.Cylinder(\n    bHollow=True,\n    dTopInnerRadius=0.005,\n    dBottomInnerRadius=0.005,\n    iPartColor=7829501)\n\nMeshEdit.Face(\n    crlFaces=[Face(7)],\n    crlFaceFixed=[],\n    iOffsetType=1,\n    dlOffset=[0.0, 0.0, 0.0],\n    dOffset=1.0,\n    dDistStrong=2.0,\n    dDistWeak=5.0)\n```"
  },
