    "text": "```python\nMeshEdit.ElementConvert(crlParts=[], iType=1)\n```\n\n## Description\n\nConvert the element type of parts.\n\n:::caution\n\nThis function is deprecated. Use [MeshEdit.SolidMesh()](MeshEdit.SolidMesh) or [MeshEdit.SurfaceMesh()](MeshEdit.SurfaceMesh) instead.\n\n:::\n\n## Inputs\n\n### `crlParts`\n\n- A _List of Cursor_ specifying the target parts.\n- The default value is [].\n\n### `iType`\n\n- An _Integer_ specifying the target element type.\n- The default value is 1.\n\n## Return Code\n\nReturns a string \"1\" if successful, or \"0\" if failed.\n\n## Sample Code\n\n```psj\nMeshEdit.ElementConvert(crlParts=[], iType=1)\n```"
