    "text": "```python\nJPT.GetScreenWidth()\n```\n\n## Description\n\nGet the width of screen window.\n\n## Inputs\n\nThis utility function does not require any input value.\n\n## Return Code\n\nAn _Integer_ specifying the width value of Main Window.\n\n## Sample Code\n\n```psj {1}\nwidth=JPT.GetScreenWidth()\nJPT.Debugger(width)\n```"
